OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FDonna Ockenden's report into "toxic"
OL,7,Fmaternity services at Nottingham
OL,8,FUniversity Hospitals NHS Trust is the
OL,9,Flatest in a long list of inquiries
OL,10,Fexposing failings in England's
OL,11,Fmaternity services.
OL,13,FAside from the devastating fact that
OL,14,Fhundreds of mothers and babies
OL,15,Fsuffered harm or died because of
OL,16,Ffailures, perhaps one of the most
OL,17,Fdisturbing findings is the
OL,18,Fdepressingly familiar theme in NHS
OL,19,Fmaternity scandals of "cover-up" and
OL,20,F"victim-blaming".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
