OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782312494
OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FIn her report, Ockenden writes in
OL,7,Fbold, with an exclamation mark, that
OL,8,Fthis "culture of compounding of harm
OL,9,Fneeds to stop!".
OL,11,FDespite plenty of policies and pledges
OL,12,Ffrom governments and the NHS, the data
OL,13,Freveals a worrying picture of the UK's
OL,14,Fmaternity services.
OL,16,FFormer Health Secretary Jeremy Hunt
OL,17,Fset a national ambition to halve the
OL,18,Frate of maternal deaths by 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
