CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782312494
OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FBut the latest statistics shows the
OL,7,Frate of women dying during or soon
OL,8,Fafter pregnancy in the UK has actually
OL,9,Fincreased by 20% over the last decade.
OL,11,FAnd the inequalities are stark. In the
OL,12,FUK, Black women are nearly three times
OL,13,Fas likely to die during pregnancy and
OL,14,Fchildbirth compared to white women.
OL,15,FWhile women living in the most
OL,16,Fdeprived areas are more than twice as
OL,17,Flikely to die.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
