CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782312494
OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FConcerns about staffing are repeatedly
OL,7,Fraised; in a recent survey by the
OL,8,FRoyal College of Midwives, 87% of
OL,9,Fmidwives said their maternity units
OL,10,Fwere not safely staffed.
OL,12,FAnd yet, according recent research,
OL,13,Falmost one in three midwifery
OL,14,Fgraduates can't find a job in the NHS.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
