CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782312494
OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FAnd of course, failings don't just
OL,7,Fcost lives - last year the NHS
OL,8,Fmaternity negligence bill was an
OL,9,Fenormous #1.3 billion, that's almost
OL,10,Fhalf all NHS negligence payouts.
OL,12,FLet alone the immeasurable emotional
OL,13,Fand psychological cost to families.
OL,15,FIn response to Ockenden's report, the
OL,16,Fgovernment announced that Martha's
OL,17,FRule - allowing parents to request a
OL,18,Frapid review from an independent
OL,19,Fmedical team - will be rolled out
OL,20,Facross all maternity wards in England.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
