PN,30506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782312494
OL,3,C'Toxic' NHS maternity services prove
OL,4,Clessons not being learnt
OL,6,FThe Department of Health also
OL,7,Fannounced that NHS staff who refuse to
OL,8,Fco-operate with future maternity
OL,9,Finquiries could face up to two years
OL,10,Fin prison.
OL,12,FNext week, we'll hear recommendations
OL,13,Ffrom a national investigation into
OL,14,FEngland's maternity services, but
OL,15,Fcampaigners say we need a judge-led
OL,16,Fstatutory public inquiry.
OL,18,FClearly, mothers, babies, midwives and
OL,19,Four health service need this to be a
OL,20,Fturning point.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
